name: Froggy Invaders (Mini Jam 106 Edition)
description:
The Frogs and their wacky technology are attacking an Ant Hole and your goal is to defend your fellow ants, using the powerful (and muddy?) AntZooka against them and their bosses.

(Note: This game is original and was made in 72 hours for the "Mini Jam 106" Contest. It might become an actual game, so stay tuned!)
